title: Ep 154: 5 Reasons Why Casey Anthony MIGHT Be Innocent
description: The trial of accused child murdered Casey Anthony is over and Casey was found not guilty.  Most people are extremely upset because she appeared to be guilty for many reasons.  I give you 5 reasons why Casey Anthony might not be guilty.  None of these are based on evidence, but instead on what might be going on inside your mind that made you think she was guilty.  Caution: open mindedness required!
